Borussia Dortmund beat Paderborn 3-0 in their Bundesliga clash at Signal Iduna Park . 
  Henrikh Mkhitaryan and Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang scored for the home side . 
  Jurgen Klopp announced he will leave the club at the end of the season . 
  Shinji Kagawa added a second for the hosts in the second half . 
 